window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The 2020 updated version of the best-selling guide to mastering communication, using conversation skills, emotional intelligence, body language, and more.</p> <p><b>“....this book makes becoming an expert conversationalist easy to understand and more importantly easy and quick to achieve” (Michael Woods, author and speaker)</b></p> <p>Cutting through the nonsense, this book offers a simple and easy to understand solution to mastering conversation and people skills using a variety of skills. No fancy gimmicks, just solid, actionable and proven advice.</p> <p>“It is rare we come across a book so direct and so effective.” (<i>Sydney Morning</i>, March 2020)</p> <p><b>Some of the topics covered in this book include:</b></p> <ul> <li>Steps to better conversation skills for any situation</li> <li>The secret to creating flowing conversations</li> <li>Master body language</li> <li>Conversation starters</li> <li>How to read other people and know what they want</li> <li>Effective speaking and listening</li> <li>Master social and emotional intelligence</li> <li>Charisma: how to improve it and how to use it</li> <li>Simple ways to improve your conflict management skills</li> <li>How to be more assertive</li> <li>Becoming a more flexible person</li> <li>How to be an expert negotiator!</li> <li>Building rapport with people</li> <li>And so much more!</li> </ul> <p><b>“A superb and life-changing book.” (Michelle Larkin, businesswomen and speaker)</b></p>"; 
